aboutMe.text:
I am a junior software engineer with 2 years of experience (including internships in large French companies) passionate about new technologies and always looking for challenges to improve my skills&nbsp;  
Thanks to my past experiences as a Full-Stack engineer or as a student engineer (UTT and KAIST), I was able to develop frontend clients with the three main SPA frameworks (**React, Vue and Angular**) as well as their main associated libraries (**Next.js, Redux, Nuxt, etc.**) but also backends based on Node.js (**Nest.js, Hapi, Strapi**) or **Java/Kotlin (Spring)** .&nbsp;  
In the mobile environment, I was also able to develop applications based on **React Native** (Android/Ios) or **Kotlin** (Android).&nbsp;  
Having started in small teams with various skills, I was also able to develop **CI/CD** skills using tools such as **Gitlab CI, Docker** as well as **AWS or GCP** (environment preparation, testing, deployment, etc.)&nbsp;  
Because of my curious nature, I started to learn new technologies during the last months to open my knowledge: **Rust, Flutter, Python**.
